name: Emily Jarecki
title: Software Developer
about: I like to create complete web applications using API systems with dynamic user interfaces.
landing: In 2021 I got a Bachelor's Degree in English!
After that, in my free time I toyed around with coding and decided to make the leap into the world of software engineering👩🏼‍💻
I enrolled in General Assembly's Software Engineering Immersive.
The imposter syndrome was CRAAAZZZYYYY. Me? A Software Engineer? What will people think of me?😬
Regardless, I completed the coding bootcamp with my head down but my eyes looking forward.
Front-End. Back-End. Full-Stack. I've gone through each challenge and continue to learn more.
Now looking for a new place to grow.🌱
